quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  58,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  58,1,( ae paighambar ) jo aurat tum se apne shohar ke baray mein behas Jaddal karti aur khuda se shikayat ( ranj o malaal ) karti thi. khuda ne is ki iltija sun li aur khuda tum dono ki guftagu sun raha tha. kuch shak nahi ke khuda santa daikhta hai
  58,2,jo log tum mein se apni aurton ko maa keh dete hain woh un ki maaen nahi ( hojatin ). un ki maaen to wohi hain jin ke batan se woh peda hue. be shak woh namaqool aur jhooti baat kehte hain aur khuda bara maaf karne wala ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  58,3,aur jo log apni biwion ko maa keh bathain phir apne qoul se rujoo karlen to ( un ko ) hum bistar honay se pehlay aik ghulam azad karna ( zurori ) hai. ( momino ) is ( hukum ) se tum ko nasiyaat ki jati hai. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is se khabardaar hai
  58,4,jis ko ghulam nah miley woh mujamat se pehlay mutawatar do mahinay ke rozay ( rakhay ) jis ko is ka bhi Maqdoor nah howa ( usay ) saath miskeeno ko khana khilana ( chahiye ). yeh ( hukum ) is liye ( hai ) ke tum khuda aur uskay rasool ke farmanbardar hojao. aur yeh khuda ki hade hain. aur nah maan-ne walon ke liye dard dainay wala azaab hai
  58,5,jo log khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat karte hain woh ( isi terhan ) zaleel kiye jayen ge jis terhan un se pehlay log zaleel kiye gay they aur hum ne saaf aur Sarih ayatain nazil kar di hain. jo nahi mantay un ko zillat ka azaab hoga
  58,6,jis din khuda un sab ko jala uthaye ga to jo kaam woh karte rahay un ko jitye ga. khuda ko woh sab ( kaam ) yaad hain aur yeh un ko bhool gay hain aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  58,7,kiya tum ko maloom nahi ke jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai khuda ko sab maloom hai. ( kisi jagah ) teen ( shakhson ) ka ( majmaa aur ) kaanon mein Salah vmshorh nahi hota magar woh un mein choutha hota hai aur nah kahin paanch ka magar woh un mein chhata hota hai aur nah is se kam ya ziyada magar woh un ke sath hota hai khuwa woh kahin hon. phir jo jo kaam yeh karte rahay hain qayamat ke din woh ( aik aik ) un ko betaye ga. be shak khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  58,8,kiya tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jin ko sargoshian karne se manakiya gaya tha. phir jis ( kaam ) se manakiya gaya tha wohi phir karne lagey aur yeh to gunah aur zulm aur rasool ( khuda ) ki nafarmani ki sargoshian karte hain. aur jab tumahray paas atay hain to jis ( kalme ) se khuda ne tum ko dua nahi di is se tumhe dua dete hain. aur apne dil mein kehte hain ke ( agar yeh waqai paighambar hain to ) jo kuch hum kehte hain khuda hamein is ki saza kyun nahi deta? ( ae paighambar ) un ko dozakh ( hi ki saza ) kaafi hai. yeh isi mein daakhil hon ge. aur woh buri jagah hai
  58,9,momino! jab tum aapas mein sargoshian karne lagu to gunah aur zayad-ti aur paighambar ki nafarmani ki baatein nah karna balkay نneko kariaur parhaiz gari ki baatein karna. aur khuda se jis ke samnay jama kiye jao ge drtay rehna
  58,10,kafiroon ki ) sargoshian to shetan ( ki harkaat ) se hain ( jo ) is liye ( ki jati hain ) ke momin ( un se ) ghumnaak hon magar khuda ke hukum ke siwa un se inhen kuch nuqsaan nahi poanch sakta. to momino ko chahiye ke khuda hi par bharosa rakhen
  58,11,momino! jab tum se kaha jaye ke majlis mein khil kar betho to khil betha karo. khuda tum ko kushadgi bakhshay ga. aur jab kaha jaye ke aُth kharray ho to aُth kharray howa karo. jo log tum mein se imaan laaye hain aur jin ko ilm ataakiya gaya hai khuda un ke darjay buland kere ga. aur khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  58,12,momino! jab tum paighambar ke kaan mein koi baat kaho to baat kehnay se pehlay ( msakin ko ) kuch khairaat day diya karo. yeh tumahray liye bohat behtar aur pakizgee ki baat hai. aur agar khairaat tum ko muyassar nah aeye to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  58,13,kiya tum is se ke paighambar ke kaan mein koi baat kehnay se pehlay khairaat diya karo dar gay? phir jab tum ne ( aisa ) nahkiya aur khuda ne tumhe maaf kardiya to namaz parhte aur zakaat dete raho aur khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari karte raho. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is se khabardaar hai
  58,14,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo aison se dosti karte hain jin par khuda ka ghazab howa. woh nah tum mein hain nah un mein. aur jaan boojh kar jhooti baton par kasmain khatay hain
  58,15,khuda ne un ke liye sakht azaab tayyar kar rakha hai. yeh jo kuch karte hain yaqeenan bura hai
  58,16,unhon ne apni qasmon ko dhaal bana liya aur ( logon ko ) khuda ke rastay se rok diya hai so un ke liye zillat ka azaab hai
  58,17,khuda ke ( azaab ke ) samnay nah to un ka maal hi kuch kaam aeye ga aur nah aulaad hi ( kuch faida day gi ). yeh log ahal dozakh hain is mein hamesha ( jaltay ) rahen ge
  58,18,jis din khuda un sab ko jala uthaye ga to jis terhan tumahray samnay kasmain khatay ( isi terhan ) khuda ke samnay kasmain khayen ge aur khayaal karen ge ke ( aisa karne se ) kaam le niklay hain. dekho yeh jhutay ( aur brsr ghalat ) hain
  58,19,shetan ne un ko qaboo mein karliya hai. aur khuda ki yaad un ko bhala di hai. yeh ( jamaat ) shetan ka lashkar hai. aur sun rakho ke shetan ka lashkar nuqsaan uthany wala hai
  58,20,jo log khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat karte hain woh nihayat zaleel hon ge
  58,21,khuda ka hukum Natiq hai ke mein aur mere paighambar zaroor ghalib rahen ge. be shak khuda zorawar ( aur ) zabardast hai
  58,22,jo log khuda par aur roz qayamat par imaan rakhtay hain tum un ko khuda aur is ke rasool ke dushmanon se dosti karte hue nah dekho ge. khuwa woh un ke baap ya betay ya bhai ya khandan hi ke log hon. yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon mein khuda ne imaan ( pathar par lakeer ki terhan ) tehreer kardiya hai aur Faiz ghaibi se un ki madad ki hai. aur woh un ko bahishtoon mein jin ke taley nehrain beh rahi hain daakhil kere ga hamesha un mein rahen ge. khuda un se khush aur woh khuda se khush. yahi giroh khuda ka lashkar hai. ( aur ) sun rakho ke khuda hi ka lashkar morad haasil karne wala hai
